import React from "react"; import { Container, Row, Col } from "react-bootstrap"; import myImg from "../../Assets/Personal/image.png"; import Tilt from "react-parallax-tilt"; import { AiFillGithub, AiFillInstagram, AiOutlineFacebook, } from "react-icons/ai"; import { FaLinkedinIn } from "react-icons/fa"; function Home2() { return (

Here's a quick Introduction:)

I'm a{" "} Computer Science and Engineering {" "} senior undergraduate at Indian Institute of Technology, Bombay. Mind you, that may sound like I'm geeky but I'm almost always up for conversations, long drives, walks and ofcourse shopping!

Owing to my CS background, I'm proficent in C++ and Python. I'm fluent in frontent technologies like React JS, Redux and Anuglar. I'm super interested in Machine Learning, Image Processing and Natural Language Processing and have had a chance to work on these through various courses, projects and internships which you can look up in the{" "} Project {" "} section.

Though poles apart from CS, I'm doing in a Minor in Enterprenurship from the{" "} Desai Seth School of Enterprenurship . Call it The Pitchers or The Social Network, that lit the intial entreprenurial fire in me, I plan to do something big (exactly how is unknown to me as well)! I own the startup{" "} FeMeal {" "} where we aim to reduce the sufferings of women who have PCOS - Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome affecting every 1 in 5 women in India.

I'm in the Autonomous Subdivision of the{" "} Mars Rover Technical Team , IIT Bombay. For a fact, we don't send people to mars! I work on designing path planning algorithms for the autnomous operation of the rover in Maritan terrains.

This year, I've had a chance to explore research. I'm doing my summer internship at the Indiana University, Bloomington, USA under{" "} Prof. Christina Chung {" "} in Human Computer Interaction and Machine Learning. I'm also working under{" "} Prof. Shankaranarayanan S {" "} from the Physics Department, IIT Bombay on a project where we are trying to use Machine Learning to come up with black hole solutions in General Relativity and beyound. Oh and I'm also the Department Research Coordinator for the CSE Department in the UG Academic Council, IIT Bombay.

I can go on for so long (that's what she said?) here but then what would my{" "} About {" "} Page do? So, I'll stop here telling a random fact, which is that even though I come from Delhi (okay Delhi NCR) but my heart lies in Mumbai xD!

Connect with me here

); } export default Home2;
